{"type":"message","id":"e7587485","parentId":"684ef961","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:10:42.233Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Needs the keyring password. Let me check if there's a GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD set or if there's a way to handle this. The user might need to provide the keyring password. Let me check if there's a way to set this up.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Tem uma conta configurada (`cod4oc@gmail.com`), mas o `gog` precisa de uma senha de keyring pra destravar os tokens. Podes definir a variável `GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD`?\n\nTenta rodar no teu terminal:\n```\nexport GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD=\"sua-senha\"\ngog calendar events primary --from 2026-02-25 --to 2026-03-01\n```\n\nOu se preferires, me passa a senha e eu rodo por ti."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":8,"output":199,"cacheRead":14753,"cacheWrite":171,"totalTokens":15131,"cost":{"input":0.000024,"output":0.0029850000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0044259,"cacheWrite":0.00064125,"total":0.00807615}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771999837152}}
